title: Mirillis Action! 1.24.2 with Loader
description:
Hello again everyone!

I've found new stuff for you - the Mirillis Action! 1.24.2, and this time - with Loader!

I've tried the loader, and it's working perfectly fine for me.

The loader was created by JohnWho in nsane.forums, big thanks to him for making this!

What I'm adding here:
1) Install file;
2) All three versions of loader.

Before using (and saying "OMG DIS DOZNT WOK GIVZ MY ERRORZ WHN LANCHIN"), please read the ReadMe file I've written, it has most stuff there.

As always, if there are any problems or anything, let me know in the comments.

(Also, I forgot to provide the VirusScan for these loaders, but my Kaspersky didn't give any warnings or Virus alerts.)

Enjoy!
